<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Website Project Payment Successful</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f4f7fa; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #48bb78 0%, #38a169 100%); padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; color: #ffffff; }
        .header h1 { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700; }
        .header p { font-size: 16px; opacity: 0.95; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .greeting { font-size: 18px; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.7; }
        .success-badge { background: #c6f6d5; color: #22543d; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 50px; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .info-box { background: #f7fafc; border-left: 4px solid #48bb78; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 6px; }
        .info-box h3 { color: #2d3748; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 600; }
        .info-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 0; }
        .info-label { font-weight: 600; color: #4a5568; min-width: 140px; }
        .info-value { color: #2d3748; flex: 1; word-break: break-word; }
        .amount-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #edf2f7 0%, #e2e8f0 100%); padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; }
        .amount-label { color: #4a5568; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .amount-value { color: #2d3748; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; }
        .timeline { background: #fef5e7; border-left: 4px solid #f39c12; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 6px; }
        .timeline h3 { color: #b7791f; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 600; }
        .timeline-step { margin-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 24px; position: relative; }
        .timeline-step:before { content: "‚úì"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #48bb78; font-weight: bold; }
        .timeline-step.pending:before { content: "‚è≥"; color: #f39c12; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 16px 32px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; }
        .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3); }
        .note { background: #e6fffa; border-left: 4px solid #38b2ac; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 6px; color: #234e52; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer { background: #f7fafc; padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: #718096; font-size: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .footer p { margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .logo { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container { margin: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
            .header { padding: 30px 20px; }
            .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
            .header h1 { font-size: 24px; }
            .info-row { flex-direction: column; }
            .info-label { min-width: auto; margin-bottom: 4px; }
            .amount-value { font-size: 28px; }
            .btn { display: block; width: 100%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üéâ</div>
            <h1>Payment Successful!</h1>
            <p>Your website project is ready to begin</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <span class="success-badge">‚úÖ Initial Payment Confirmed</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello <%= companyName %>,
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #4a5568; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                Great news! We've successfully received your initial payment for the website project. Your project is now ready to begin development! üöÄ
            </p>
            
            <div class="amount-box">
                <div class="amount-label">Amount Paid (50%)</div>
                <div class="amount-value">$<%= amountPaid.toFixed(2) %></div>
                <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 8px;">CAD</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>üìã Project Details</h3>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Domain Name:</span>
                    <span class="info-value"><strong><%= domainName %></strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Selected Plan:</span>
                    <span class="info-value"><%= planName %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Total Amount:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">$<%= totalAmount.toFixed(2) %> CAD</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Paid (50%):</span>
                    <span class="info-value">$<%= amountPaid.toFixed(2) %> CAD</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Remaining (50%):</span>
                    <span class="info-value">$<%= remainingAmount.toFixed(2) %> CAD</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Payment Date:</span>
                    <span class="info-value"><%= paymentDate %></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline">
                <h3>üóìÔ∏è What Happens Next?</h3>
                <div class="timeline-step">Payment received and confirmed</div>
                <div class="timeline-step pending">Our team will start working on your website</div>
                <div class="timeline-step pending">You'll receive regular progress updates</div>
                <div class="timeline-step pending">Upon completion, you'll pay the remaining 50%</div>
                <div class="timeline-step pending">Your website will be launched!</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="note">
                <strong>üí° Stay Connected:</strong> You can track your project progress, communicate with our team, and view updates in your project dashboard.
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="btn">
                    View Project Dashboard
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
                <strong>Need help?</strong> Our support team is available to assist you with any questions about your website project.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Canadian Bazaar</strong></p>
            <p>Building your online presence</p>
            <p style="color: #a0aec0; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 12px;">
                This is an automated notification. For support, please contact us through your dashboard.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

